Loki Laufeyson is a lot of things, but could he rule the free world? That's the premise of the 2016 4-issue miniseries "Vote Loki", which was written by Christopher Hastings for Marvel Comics. A loose commentary on the dumpster fire that was the 2016 Presidential Election, "Vote Loki" serves as both a cautionary tale AND a self-fulfilling prophecy, as it examines what happens when political candidates become cults of personality. Could Loki's lying ways lead him to the most powerful seat in America? Join us, and find out!

